content: A pet store in Urumqi released a video showing that at today's Urumqi epidemic prevention and control press conference, an official "promoted" the pet store. The video attracted widespread attention from netizens and was jokingly called "This epidemic prevention and control press conference was exclusively sponsored by Xinjiang Xiaozuzong Pet Products Store."

name: 李老师不是你老师
